# === Heavy raw image originals ===
# The site serves the optimised .jpg files in images/ai/. Raw PNG sources where an
# optimised .jpg twin already exists must not be committed (e.g. the removed hero-day.png).
# Do NOT add a blanket *.png ignore — the site uses real .png assets (logos, certs).
# FLAGGED + excluded from this push: unused 10MB raw brand photo (portrait, too big for OG). Optimise to .jpg before using.
images/real/clip11-egr-brand.png

# Raw Higgsfield generation dumps (images/ai/hf_*.png) — ~30MB each, ~1.4GB total.
# Scratch only; the site serves the named, optimised images/ai/*.jpg files. Never commit these.
images/ai/hf_*.png

# Raw camera/phone dumps in images/real/ (unreferenced, unoptimised originals).
# These patterns target the raw-dump naming ONLY — properly NAMED real images
# (e.g. images/real/og-solar.jpg, images/real/ground-mount-install.jpg) are NOT
# ignored and can be committed normally.
images/real/DJI_*
images/real/dji_fly_*
images/real/WhatsApp Image*
images/real/Agri.jpg
images/real/2.jpg
images/real/3.jpg
